[SPEAKER_00] je društvena razina.

1058
00:34:11,739 --> 00:34:15,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je što Bog želi od nas

1059
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj okolini.

1060
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:18,780
[SPEAKER_00] U našem društvu.

1061
00:34:19,039 --> 00:34:20,260
[SPEAKER_00] Među našim prijateljima.

1062
00:34:20,260 --> 00:34:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] Prema siromašnjima.

1063
00:34:23,039 --> 00:34:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] Prema odbačenima.

1064
00:34:24,239 --> 00:34:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] Šta Bog od mene tu želi.

1065
00:34:26,659 --> 00:34:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je važna razina.

1066
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kršćani ne smijemo biti zatvoreni

1067
00:34:31,159 --> 00:34:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] u sva četiri zida.

1068
00:34:32,079 --> 00:34:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] To nije kršćanstvo.

1069
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajmo prvu crkvu.

1070
00:34:35,340 --> 00:34:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se jesu skupljeni na sasancima.

1071
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali su konstantno bili među drugima.

1072
00:34:39,539 --> 00:34:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna od glavnih zadaća crkve

1073
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] prvog vremena je bila briga

1074
00:34:43,059 --> 00:34:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] za one koji su napušteni.

1075
00:34:44,599 --> 00:34:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] Koji su siromašni.

1076
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] Mi to ne bi.

1077
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] Nama je lijepo slaviti.

1078
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:52,239
[SPEAKER_00] I ona ti tu bude neko pijan na cestu.

1079
00:34:52,239 --> 00:34:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] Iju.

1080
00:34:54,579 --> 00:34:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bih mu poznali ni hitnutom čovjeku.

1081
00:34:58,639 --> 00:35:04,280
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje tu su stvaranje društva?

1082
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:08,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi kršćani nećemo biti promjena u ovom društvu.

1083
00:35:08,239 --> 00:35:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali promjena koja ne minja stvari

1084
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] prosvjedima, referendumima i ne znam ja čime.

1085
00:35:13,579 --> 00:35:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nego promjena koja daje konkretnu ljubav drugom čovjeku.

1086
00:35:18,559 --> 00:35:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] Na taj način, na taj način mijenjamo svijet.

1087
00:35:20,980 --> 00:35:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] Na taj način.

1088
00:35:23,139 --> 00:35:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se ja ne mogu nasmijati nekome

1089
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji vidim da je potreban osmijeh.

1090
00:35:27,559 --> 00:35:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne mogu zagrliti nekoga.

1091
00:35:29,159 --> 00:35:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] Pa već na taj način ja mijenjam druge oko sebe.

1092
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koliko puta mi se dogodilo

1093
00:35:34,159 --> 00:35:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] da bi imao predrasudu prema nekom.

1094
00:35:36,239 --> 00:35:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] I onda bi si uzelo za žrtvu.

1095
00:35:39,199 --> 00:35:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] E sad ću baš na silu davati ljubav.

1096
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] To je osoba koju ne osjećam, živcira me ono.

1097
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:46,340
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta?

1098
00:35:46,340 --> 00:35:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bog bi razbio, na kraju su mi ti ljudi postali najbolji prijatelji.

1099
00:35:54,179 --> 00:35:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] Zaista vam govorim.

1100
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zamislimo da tako živimo kršanski prema svima oko nas.

1101
00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:04,739
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko bi više prodora ljubavi išlo od jednih do drugih.

1102
00:36:04,739 --> 00:36:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto bi se počelo mijenjati.

1103
00:36:06,579 --> 00:36:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] A znate šta?

1104
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem da 90%,

1105
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] dobro, 70%.

1106
00:36:12,579 --> 00:36:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si pomislio, stvari o čem pričaš ti.

1107
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:17,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ide to tako lako.

1108
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] To je naš problem.

1109
00:36:20,079 --> 00:36:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] Mi što god trebamo krenuti, raditi, mijenjati.

1110
00:36:23,380 --> 00:36:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] A, ko će to?

1111
00:36:25,960 --> 00:36:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] To nije stav kršćana.

1112
00:36:28,099 --> 00:36:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] To nije stav kršćana.

1113
00:36:31,219 --> 00:36:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, koliko vidim Božju riječ,

1114
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] kršćani su činili nemoguće stvari.

1115
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:38,219
[SPEAKER_00] Koje su bile totalno nonsense stvari.

1116
00:36:38,219 --> 00:36:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] Biblijski likovi su bili ljudi

1117
00:36:41,639 --> 00:36:44,219
[SPEAKER_00] koji su preokretali cijelu naciju

1118
00:36:44,219 --> 00:36:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] sa Božjim sustvaranjem.

1119
00:36:46,079 --> 00:36:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli narod su promijenili.

1120
00:36:48,500 --> 00:36:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] Božjim se su surađivali s Bogom.

1121
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:54,340
[SPEAKER_00] Cijele narode, bitke i ne znam što.

1122
00:36:54,340 --> 00:36:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su surađivali s Bogom?

1123
00:36:56,699 --> 00:36:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi krenemo, pogledajte koliko nas je.

1124
00:36:59,019 --> 00:37:01,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi krenemo ovdje danas urađivati s Bogom.

1125
00:37:01,699 --> 00:37:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znate što mi možemo napraviti u našoj okolini?

1126
00:37:04,699 --> 00:37:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ne trebamo promijeniti cijelu Europu.

1127
00:37:07,420 --> 00:37:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] Promijenimo, da nesmo promijeniti svoju obitelj.

1128
00:37:11,159 --> 00:37:12,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ne na način da ja kažem,

1129
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] mama, Luka 2.25 kaže.

1130
00:37:15,039 --> 00:37:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nego na način,

1131
00:37:18,559 --> 00:37:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] mama, mogu i ja oprati vece školjku.

1132
00:37:21,619 --> 00:37:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, to je isto sustvaranje.

1133
00:37:29,019 --> 00:37:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] Jer će se nešto počet događati u mojoj obitelji.

1134
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:33,699
[SPEAKER_00] Na poslu.

1135
00:37:33,699 --> 00:37:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da nekom dođem i kažem,

1136
00:37:35,159 --> 00:37:36,300
[SPEAKER_00] to što činiš je grijeh.

1137
00:37:36,300 --> 00:37:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] Yoga je smrtni grijeh.

1138
00:37:38,599 --> 00:37:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] Morat ćeš ići na molitvu otklinjanja.

1139
00:37:43,139 --> 00:37:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1140
00:37:43,659 --> 00:37:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] Nego prijatelju.

1141
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ti treba donijeti kavu.

1142
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:50,480
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta?

1143
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] Mi puno puta jezikom propovjedamo evanđelje,

1144
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] a u dijelu ga nemamo.

1145
00:37:56,340 --> 00:37:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Franjo Asiški kaže,

1146
00:37:58,340 --> 00:37:59,400
[SPEAKER_00] to je ono, valjda,

1147
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] nisam našao ono tjedan da se to ne izvrti

1148
00:38:02,500 --> 00:38:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] po nekim društvenim mrežama,

1149
00:38:03,659 --> 00:38:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je istina.

1150
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,980
[SPEAKER_00] Valjda nam to treba na čelo napisati.

1151
00:38:06,599 --> 00:38:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan propovjeda evanđelje,

1152
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad je potrebno,

1153
00:38:09,360 --> 00:38:10,699
[SPEAKER_00] koristi riječi.

1154
00:38:10,699 --> 00:38:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] To je sustvarateljstvo s Bogom.

1155
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] Znate zašto?

1156
00:38:14,179 --> 00:38:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] Jer će Bog u svom sustvaranju,

1157
00:38:17,159 --> 00:38:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] neće te pozvati da prozivaš tuđi grijeh.

1158
00:38:19,860 --> 00:38:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bog te to neće pozvati.

1159
00:38:22,199 --> 00:38:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] To nije sustvaranje.

1160
00:38:23,719 --> 00:38:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta će Bog pozvati?

1161
00:38:26,119 --> 00:38:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] Da opereš noge svom bratu i da ih poljubiš.

1162
00:38:28,639 --> 00:38:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je sustvaranje.

1163
00:38:30,539 --> 00:38:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je sustvaranje.

1164
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] I četvrta razina, razina crkve.

1165
00:38:36,599 --> 00:38:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja bježim od svoje župne zajednice,

1166
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi mijenio crkvu na globalnoj razini.

1167
00:38:43,739 --> 00:38:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] Papa je rekao ovo,

1168
00:38:45,159 --> 00:38:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] biskupi žive ovako,

1169
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] Vatikan onako, ovo i onako.

1170
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] A gdje sam ja?

1171
00:38:51,539 --> 00:38:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] Budi promjena koju želiš vidjeti u crkvi.

1172
00:38:54,599 --> 00:38:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi danas započnemo živjeti svetije,

1173
00:38:57,199 --> 00:38:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] crkva će za ovoliko biti svetija.

1174
00:38:59,519 --> 00:39:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne možemo to živjeti tamo

1175
00:39:03,579 --> 00:39:04,980
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je samo nama lijepo.

1176
00:39:06,300 --> 00:39:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] Super, ja kažem da ono,

1177
00:39:09,059 --> 00:39:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] doslovno smatram da svi trebaju biti

1178
00:39:10,679 --> 00:39:12,219
[SPEAKER_00] u nekim molitvenim zajednicama.

1179
00:39:12,219 --> 00:39:16,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali trebamo nešto činiti na razini crkve.

1180
00:39:16,199 --> 00:39:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako je meni samo lijepo na mojoj zajednici,

1181
00:39:18,619 --> 00:39:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] a na razini crkve ništa ne činim,

1182
00:39:21,539 --> 00:39:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] onda mi bi svi bili u pastoralnim vječima,

1183
00:39:26,079 --> 00:39:27,440
[SPEAKER_00] ekonomskom vječu.

1184
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] A ko će čistiti crkvu?

1185
00:39:29,039 --> 00:39:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znate ko je meni tu jako pomogao?

1186
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mala Terezija.

1187
00:39:33,019 --> 00:39:38,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je upravo gorela o putu svetosti,

1188
00:39:38,880 --> 00:39:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] put svetosti koji ide od malih stvari.

1189
00:39:42,599 --> 00:39:45,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ne velike stvari, male stvari.

1190
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] Mi bi svi velike stvari,

1191
00:39:47,500 --> 00:39:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] ali preskačemo te male stvari po kojima se posvećujemo.

1192
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:54,139
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo pozvani, sestre i braće, izgrađivati crkvu.

1193
00:39:54,139 --> 00:39:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pozvani smo pomoć mom župniku,

1194
00:39:57,059 --> 00:39:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] kakav god da je.

1195
00:39:58,039 --> 00:40:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ne želi našu pomoć.

1196
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] Nema veze, pozvani smo, ljubi ga.

1197
00:40:02,719 --> 00:40:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] To možeš.

1198
00:40:04,460 --> 00:40:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] To možeš.

1199
00:40:05,860 --> 00:40:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš moliti za njega.

1200
00:40:07,719 --> 00:40:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nemoj moliti za njega,

1201
00:40:09,039 --> 00:40:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine, nek se obrati,

1202
00:40:11,059 --> 00:40:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] nek doživi silu tvojega duha.

1203
00:40:13,119 --> 00:40:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

1204
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] Moli ono što Bog želi od tebe da moliš za njega.

1205
00:40:18,119 --> 00:40:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] Moli kao su stvaratelj.

1206
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pitaj gospodina, gospodine, šta treba mom župniku?

1207
00:40:24,900 --> 00:40:27,320
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mu treba?

1208
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da li mu možda treba da ja samo popričam s njim,

1209
00:40:29,599 --> 00:40:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] da ga pitam kako je?

1210
00:40:30,639 --> 00:40:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, na svećenika niko ne pita puno puta kako smo.

1211
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:36,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se znam iz njega kad mi nekog pita,

1212
00:40:36,739 --> 00:40:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] sano, Ivane, kako si ti?

1213
00:40:38,059 --> 00:40:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sano kad viže da te neko pita.

1214
00:40:39,579 --> 00:40:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš si baš što trebao reći s ovom župniku taj dan?

1215
00:40:44,260 --> 00:40:46,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ali pitaj Isusa.

1216
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa, šta treba mom župnik?

1217
00:40:47,659 --> 00:40:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je moje mjesto u crkvi?

1218
00:40:50,199 --> 00:40:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mala Terezija kad je Bog objavio gdje je njezino mjesto u crkvi.

1219
00:40:54,019 --> 00:40:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite ovo.

1220
00:40:55,119 --> 00:41:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] Čitala je, bila ni više ni manje nego korinčanima,

1221
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] službe, jedne proroke, druge za učitelje,

1222
00:41:05,019 --> 00:41:07,679
[SPEAKER_00] jedne apostole, jedni mole u jezicima,

1223
00:41:07,679 --> 00:41:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] drugi tumače, jedni ovo, jedni ono.

1224
00:41:09,900 --> 00:41:13,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna je rekla ja sebe ne vidim u ničem od ovoga.

1225
00:41:14,199 --> 00:41:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih bila sve od ovog, jer ne shvatila, ja ću biti ljubav.

1226
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to.

1227
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:24,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta mi u sustvarateljstvu trčimo za velikim stvarima,

1228
00:41:24,699 --> 00:41:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] za velikim obećanim zemljama.

1229
00:41:27,539 --> 00:41:31,260
[SPEAKER_00] Može te Bog pozivati da budeš svet u najmanjoj stvari.

1230
00:41:31,260 --> 00:41:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] Može ćeš cijeli život čistiti crkvu i jednog dana biti neraspadnu do zbog toga.

1231
00:41:38,059 --> 00:41:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] To nije nemoguće.

1232
00:41:40,300 --> 00:41:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] To nije nemoguće.

1233
00:41:42,420 --> 00:41:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] Koje su zaprekle?

1234
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] Zapreke za sustvarateljstvo.

1235
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:53,340
[SPEAKER_00] Prva, ja bih rekao, jedna od težih zapreka je kontrola.

1236
00:41:53,340 --> 00:41:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] Volimo sve kontrolirati.

1237
00:41:56,440 --> 00:41:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] To je sindrom današnjeg vremena.

1238
00:41:58,860 --> 00:42:00,639
[SPEAKER_00] Sve moram imat pod kontrolom.

1239
00:42:00,639 --> 00:42:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] Imam još vremena.

1240
00:42:03,139 --> 00:42:03,820
[SPEAKER_00] 15 minuta.

1241
00:42:03,820 --> 00:42:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj.

1242
00:42:07,219 --> 00:42:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bam.

1243
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj.

1244
00:42:14,119 --> 00:42:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kontrola.

1245
00:42:16,519 --> 00:42:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] Volimo kontrolirati stvari.

1246
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] I mora nam sve biti kako treba.

1247
00:42:23,599 --> 00:42:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] Perfekcionizam.

1248
00:42:24,940 --> 00:42:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da je Bože da pogriješim.

1249
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da je Bože da mi jedan konac ispadne iz ruke.

1250
00:42:30,500 --> 00:42:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] Šta nas je?

1251
00:42:32,460 --> 00:42:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] Anksiozno.

1252
00:42:33,260 --> 00:42:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] Strah.

1253
00:42:33,760 --> 00:42:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] Šta sad?

1254
00:42:34,440 --> 00:42:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kontrola te isto tako zatvara da budeš sustvaratelj.

1255
00:42:39,559 --> 00:42:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što ne dopuštaš Bogu da kontrolira stvari,

1256
00:42:43,039 --> 00:42:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] nego ti postaješ onaj koji kontrolira stvari i šta se dogodi dođeš do zida.

1257
00:42:48,579 --> 00:42:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne možeš sve kontrolirati.

1258
00:42:50,519 --> 00:42:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to ne pripada tebi.

1259
00:42:52,699 --> 00:42:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] To ne pripada tvom identitetu sustvaratelja.

1260
00:42:55,380 --> 00:43:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kontrola pripada identitetu stvoritelja Isusa Hrista, a ne nama.

1261
00:43:02,420 --> 00:43:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ne možemo kontrolirati tuđe živote.

1262
00:43:04,940 --> 00:43:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad vidim kako roditelji danas sa djecom, to je strašno.

1263
00:43:09,039 --> 00:43:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] On zna u period, u sekundu gdje je njegovog djete.

1264
00:43:14,420 --> 00:43:16,099
[SPEAKER_00] Sve svom djetetu isplanira.

1265
00:43:16,099 --> 00:43:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] Od tad do tad imaš japanski.

1266
00:43:19,579 --> 00:43:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] Od tad i do tad imaš, ne znam, neki nonsense, ono sport.

1267
00:43:24,139 --> 00:43:25,860
[SPEAKER_00] Od tad do tad imaš ovo.

1268
00:43:25,860 --> 00:43:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] Od tad do tad ovo.

1269
00:43:27,039 --> 00:43:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] To je strašno.

1270
00:43:28,300 --> 00:43:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] Toliko djecu smo počeli kontrolirati.

1271
00:43:31,119 --> 00:43:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] I konstanto kontroliramo.

1272
00:43:35,079 --> 00:43:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kontroliramo svoje prijatelje ljudi.

1273
00:43:38,320 --> 00:43:41,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kontroliramo zašto?

1274
00:43:41,659 --> 00:43:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] Čim vidiš da tvoj prijatelj, malo s nekim drugim, malo više,

1275
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] on nije ti baš pravo.

1276
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda kreneš manipulirat.

1277
00:43:48,960 --> 00:43:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1278
00:43:51,099 --> 00:43:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi ga mogo kontrolirat.

1279
00:43:52,539 --> 00:43:55,280
[SPEAKER_00] To su ozbiljne stvari.

1280
00:43:55,280 --> 00:43:57,139
[SPEAKER_00] To su stvari za koje se moramo kajati.

1281
00:43:57,139 --> 00:43:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam da li to znate.

1282
00:43:58,099 --> 00:44:02,719
[SPEAKER_00] Manipulacija i kontrola su vrlo ozbiljne stvari

1283
00:44:02,719 --> 00:44:04,860
[SPEAKER_00] za koje moramo ući u pokajanje.

1284
00:44:04,860 --> 00:44:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo ozbiljne stvari.

1285
00:44:07,480 --> 00:44:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mi konstanto manipuliramo drugima, tuđim emocijama.

1286
00:44:12,280 --> 00:44:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] Manipuliramo situacijama da bi doveli stvari kako mi želimo.

1287
00:44:15,539 --> 00:44:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] Šta smo napravili?

1288
00:44:17,059 --> 00:44:20,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ušli u identitet stvoritelja koji nam ne pripada.

1289
00:44:20,119 --> 00:44:21,659
[SPEAKER_00] Kakve ćemo plodove nositi?

1290
00:44:21,659 --> 00:44:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da li ćemo baštini blagoslov?

1291
00:44:23,880 --> 00:44:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] Nema sile blagoslova.

1292
00:44:25,699 --> 00:44:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kakvu silu zovemo na sebe ako nije blagoslov?

1293
00:44:28,980 --> 00:44:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je?

1294
00:44:31,079 --> 00:44:31,679
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

1295
00:44:31,679 --> 00:44:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne možemo biti kontrolori svih i svega u svom životu.

1296
00:44:37,300 --> 00:44:40,260
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ne dopuštamo sili blagoslova da se izlije u moj život.

1297
00:44:40,260 --> 00:44:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da se izlije nad moje situacije.

1298
00:44:42,539 --> 00:44:47,320
[SPEAKER_00] Mi često molimo, gospodine, ti uzmi u svoje ruke.

1299
00:44:47,320 --> 00:44:48,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi predajem.

1300
00:44:48,380 --> 00:44:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] A zapravo gvorimo, ne mići ruke.

1301
00:44:51,739 --> 00:44:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, znate šta?

1302
00:44:54,539 --> 00:44:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je stvarno tako.

1303
00:44:55,699 --> 00:45:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mi molimo da gospodin preuzme stvari, da on sve čini, ali mu ne damo.

1304
00:45:00,559 --> 00:45:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jer se bojimo šta će on napraviti.

1305
00:45:03,079 --> 00:45:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pustiti da je bolje ja to.

1306
00:45:04,460 --> 00:45:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ti mi moši dati savjet, pa ću ja vidjeti.

1307
00:45:07,880 --> 00:45:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nećemo imat plodova u svom životu na taj način.

1308
00:45:12,460 --> 00:45:14,719
[SPEAKER_00] Nećemo.

1309
00:45:14,719 --> 00:45:16,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nema sile blagoslova.

1310
00:45:16,659 --> 00:45:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to onda ne vodi on, nego vodim ja.

1311
00:45:22,739 --> 00:45:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] I to nije nešto za što me on želi.

1312
00:45:25,699 --> 00:45:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] A on, ako bude, činio kako on želi, vjerujem mi, bit će najbolje.

1313
00:45:31,019 --> 00:45:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je prva stvar.

1314
00:45:32,460 --> 00:45:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] Kontrola, manipulacija.

1315
00:45:34,199 --> 00:45:36,800
[SPEAKER_00] Strah od pogreške, perfekcionizam.

1316
00:45:36,800 --> 00:45:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] Druga stvar su nerješene rane.

1317
00:45:40,079 --> 00:45:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] Najčešće je tu rana odbačenosti.

1318
00:45:45,039 --> 00:45:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećaj manje vrijednosti.

1319
00:45:48,320 --> 00:45:52,400
[SPEAKER_00] To su rane koje trebamo konstantno.

1320
00:45:52,400 --> 00:45:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujte mi, to je koka pula.

1321
00:45:55,400 --> 00:46:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Znati, mi znamo da kad idemo na molitvu, unbound ili nešto, pa onda znamo onu ljusku koju treba s kapule maknuti.

1322
00:46:03,900 --> 00:46:07,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ali koliko je slojeva te kapule dok ne dođemo do srži?

1323
00:46:07,300 --> 00:46:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko?

1324
00:46:09,519 --> 00:46:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] I vjerujte mi, svako toliko, tražite od gospodina.

1325
00:46:13,739 --> 00:46:17,860
[SPEAKER_00] One, svako od nas ima specifičnu ranu u svom životu.

1326
00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] Može to odbačenost, možda je to, ne znam, bilo koja druga rana.

1327
00:46:22,360 --> 00:46:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] Svako ima nešto koja moja je boljka.

1328
00:46:24,760 --> 00:46:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kopajte, tražite od gospodina dublje vidjet.

1329
00:46:27,480 --> 00:46:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer često reagiramo iz tih rana.

1330
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] I na taj način zatvaramo se prema su stvarateljstvu.

1331
00:46:32,940 --> 00:46:35,780
[SPEAKER_00] Jer reagiramo, želimo zalječiti tu ranu na krivi način.

1332
00:46:37,239 --> 00:46:39,280
[SPEAKER_00] Želimo da nas vole, da ovo, da ono.

1333
00:46:39,280 --> 00:46:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se bojimo ljudskih obzira.

1334
00:46:41,380 --> 00:46:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] Šta će netko reći?

1335
00:46:42,840 --> 00:46:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] I na taj način zatvaramo protok Božje milosti.

1336
00:46:46,079 --> 00:46:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1337
00:46:46,820 --> 00:46:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jer onda ponovno mi preuzimamo stvar u svoje ruke.

1338
00:46:49,820 --> 00:46:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ulazimo u identitet stvoritelja.

1339
00:46:51,780 --> 00:46:54,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne pitamo, gospodine, kako ti to želiš?

1340
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ti želiš? Šta da napravim?

1341
00:46:56,500 --> 00:46:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] I ako i pitamo, sami sebi damo odgovor.

1342
00:46:59,380 --> 00:47:01,659
[SPEAKER_00] Uopće ne slušamo, pa kao, da, napraviću to.

1343
00:47:01,659 --> 00:47:06,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je realnost.

1344
00:47:07,239 --> 00:47:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je bitno ne bježati od svojih rana i od svoje stvarnosti,

1345
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:15,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego zalječiti to, da mogu potpuno služiti gospodinu

1346
00:47:15,960 --> 00:47:20,360
[SPEAKER_00] i da mogu biti su stvaratelj u svemu za što me gospodin želi.

1347
00:47:20,360 --> 00:47:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tako isto, kod svih ovih, hoci će imanje vrijednosti,

1348
00:47:24,820 --> 00:47:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] posebno rane obitelji, odnos s otcem, s majkom.

1349
00:47:30,059 --> 00:47:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] To su sve nekakve s profesorima u osnovnoj školi,

1350
00:47:35,320 --> 00:47:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] u srednjoj školi.

1351
00:47:36,780 --> 00:47:40,599
[SPEAKER_00] Sve su to stvari koje trebamo donositi gospodinu za lječit,

1352
00:47:40,599 --> 00:47:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] da bimo mogli biti kodati u identitetu su stvaratelja.

1353
00:47:44,980 --> 00:47:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] Koji su koraci?

1354
00:47:49,539 --> 00:48:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam uzeo korake, mi je gospodin objavio iz jedne možda stvari koje nekad ne bi ni vidio

1355
00:48:00,440 --> 00:48:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] i nedavno mi je gospodin savio u srce da čitam postanak.

1356
00:48:06,940 --> 00:48:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] je onako postanak. Šta ću s postankom opet?

1357
00:48:10,340 --> 00:48:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] Daj, zove me na Jošu, zove me nešto ono, ali postanak.

1358
00:48:15,099 --> 00:48:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] I nije mi bilo jasno dok trenutka, dok nisam došao do ovog dijela.

1359
00:48:20,880 --> 00:48:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] Znači to je dio, vjerovatno, koji ja prije nikad nisam ni primijetio.

1360
00:48:26,699 --> 00:48:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] A to je dio kada Abraham je na kraju svog života

1361
00:48:30,940 --> 00:48:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] i zove svoga slugu, svojeg glavnog slugu, najstarijeg slugu,

1362
00:48:37,780 --> 00:48:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji, njegov sluga, ima vlast nad svom Abrahamovom imovinom.

1363
00:48:46,019 --> 00:48:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači moramo voliti računati da je to ogromna imovina.

1364
00:48:49,079 --> 00:48:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] I on ga zove i traži da ode po ženu njegovom sinu.

1365
00:48:58,440 --> 00:49:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] I on mu je poslušan.

1366
00:49:01,400 --> 00:49:06,219
[SPEAKER_00] Nije morao to napraviti jer je realno mogo uzeti sebi svoju imovinu.

1367
00:49:06,219 --> 00:49:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] On ostaje vjeran Abrahamu.

1368
00:49:09,760 --> 00:49:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] I tu mi je gospodin pokazao određene korake u sustvarateljstvu

1369
00:49:14,539 --> 00:49:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji su mene fascinirali.

1370
00:49:15,940 --> 00:49:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve nešto što mi znamo.

1371
00:49:19,079 --> 00:49:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prva stvar je molitva.

1372
00:49:21,000 --> 00:49:26,780
[SPEAKER_00] Mi vrlo često ulazimo u nekakvo djelovanje,

1373
00:49:26,780 --> 00:49:29,860
[SPEAKER_00] u nekakve odluke u svom životu bez molitve.

1374
00:49:29,860 --> 00:49:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] Mi možda molimo, ali i molimo na način da gospodin blagoslovi našu odluku,

1375
00:49:35,719 --> 00:49:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] da blagoslovi nešto što smo mi odlučili.

1376
00:49:38,039 --> 00:49:40,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi ne pitamo gospodine što ti želiš.

1377
00:49:40,820 --> 00:49:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] Prva stvar je da ja pitam gospodine što ti želiš.

1378
00:49:44,119 --> 00:49:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] Što želiš za tu konkretnu situaciju?

1379
00:49:47,440 --> 00:49:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] Abrahamov sluga kada moli,

1380
00:49:49,480 --> 00:49:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] on traži od gospodina Božju volju.

1381
00:49:53,380 --> 00:49:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ne traži svoju volju,

1382
00:49:56,440 --> 00:49:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] nego traži Božju volju.

1383
00:49:59,820 --> 00:50:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Druga stvar nije djelovanje, nego slušanje.

1384
00:50:06,199 --> 00:50:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono gdje mi najčešće, najjače zastranimo.

1385
00:50:11,679 --> 00:50:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] Mi očekujemo da će nam Bog uvijek govoriti,

1386
00:50:17,360 --> 00:50:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bog govori na taj način, ne možemo to negirati.

1387
00:50:20,199 --> 00:50:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Posledno, oni koji imaju proročka pomazanja,

1388
00:50:23,539 --> 00:50:28,179
[SPEAKER_00] Bog im jako govori direktno kroz slike,

1389
00:50:28,179 --> 00:50:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] kroz određene spoznaje i tako dalje.

1390
00:50:31,059 --> 00:50:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to je dobro.

1391
00:50:33,000 --> 00:50:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] Vi koji rastete u proročkom pomazanju,

1392
00:50:35,300 --> 00:50:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji imate nekog od vas nadgleda,

1393
00:50:37,579 --> 00:50:38,820
[SPEAKER_00] rastite i dalje u tome.

1394
00:50:38,820 --> 00:50:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] Koristite to.

1395
00:50:39,900 --> 00:50:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bog to želi dat svakome.

1396
00:50:41,199 --> 00:50:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] To nije samo za pojedince.

1397
00:50:42,800 --> 00:50:46,360
[SPEAKER_00] Oni koji se možda još nisu dobro istrenirali

1398
00:50:46,360 --> 00:50:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] u proročkom pomazanju,

1399
00:50:47,539 --> 00:50:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] onda je dobro vidjeti koji su načini kako Bog govori.

1400
00:50:51,400 --> 00:50:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] Bog najprije govori po svoje riječi.

1401
00:50:54,539 --> 00:50:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, moram čitat Božiju riječ.

1402
00:50:56,380 --> 00:50:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se ne družim s Božijom riječi,

1403
00:50:58,039 --> 00:50:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] neću upoznat Božiji govor.

1404
00:50:59,579 --> 00:51:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] Neću naučit kao je to način kako Bog govori.

1405
00:51:02,400 --> 00:51:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže poslanica Hebraima da je živa i dijelotvorna Božija riječ.

1406
00:51:06,500 --> 00:51:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] A to da je Božija riječ živa,

1407
00:51:08,340 --> 00:51:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] znači da je njegova riječ živa i za moje konkretne situacije,

1408
00:51:11,440 --> 00:51:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] i za moje vrijeme.

1409
00:51:12,320 --> 00:51:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja ne čitam Božiju riječ,

1410
00:51:15,659 --> 00:51:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] a očekujem da mi Bog govori,

1411
00:51:17,179 --> 00:51:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] na koji način će mi Bog govorit?

1412
00:51:18,880 --> 00:51:20,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ne mogu ni prepoznat njegov govor.

1413
00:51:21,460 --> 00:51:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] Da, Bog će ponekad učiniti nekakve izvanredne situacije,

1414
00:51:24,139 --> 00:51:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] da će mi progovorit kroz nekoga i tako dalje.

1415
00:51:26,599 --> 00:51:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ali Bog tebi želi osobno progovorit,

1416
00:51:29,500 --> 00:51:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] kroz svoju riječ najprije.

1417
00:51:31,099 --> 00:51:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] To je prva stvar.

1418
00:51:32,260 --> 00:51:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] Čitanje Božije riječi je osnova,

1419
00:51:34,599 --> 00:51:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] osnova u odnosu u relaciji s Bogom.

1420
00:51:37,659 --> 00:51:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] Druga stvar je moja savjest.

1421
00:51:40,739 --> 00:51:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ti govori preko tvoje savjesti.

1422
00:51:43,019 --> 00:51:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] Mi učimo djecu u prvom osnovne,

1423
00:51:45,519 --> 00:51:48,000
